flowchart TD
    A[User authenticates with approved RSU email] --> B[Supabase Authentication]
    B --> C[Open RSU Nexus frontend]
    C --> D{Choose an action}

    D -->|Create listing| E[Validate listing form]
    E -->|Invalid| F[Show field-specific error]
    E -->|Valid| G[Save listing in Supabase PostgreSQL]
    G --> H[Store approved image in Supabase Storage]
    G --> I[Show listing-created confirmation]

    D -->|Browse| J[Load active marketplace listings]
    J --> K[Search / Filter]
    K --> L[Open listing details]
    L --> M[Submit request]
    M --> N[Save request with Pending status]
    N --> O[Show confirmation and request status]

    D -->|Manage records| P{Authorized owner or admin?}
    P -->|No| Q[Deny update]
    P -->|Yes| R[Update owned listing, request status, or moderated record]
    R --> S[Refresh dashboard and marketplace]

    T[Supabase Row Level Security] --> G
    T --> J
    T --> N
    T --> R
